    <item>
      <title>交易所交易的外汇衍生品可能会受到印度央行新法规的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/exchange-traded-fx-derivatives-may-be-hit-by-new-rbi-regulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，印度央行已确认，与卢比挂钩的交易所交易货币衍生品合约只能用于对冲目的，此前印度央行对低于 1 亿美元的头寸允许进行非对冲交易感到困惑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/exchange-traded-fx-derivatives-may-be-hit-by-new-rbi-regulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 10:37:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
