      <title>欧洲央行行长霍尔兹曼不会寻求连任奥地利央行行长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/ecb-s-holzmann-won-t-seek-second-term-as-austrian-bank-governor</link>
